Finance::Currency::Convert::XE
==============================

This module is a Perl extension for currency conversion available from
XE.com's Universal Currency Converter (tm) site.

The module was originally named WWW::UCC, but upon discovering the
distribution Finance::Currency::Convert::Yahoo, felt it would better fit
into that namespace.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

  WWW::Mechanize
  HTML::TokeParser

For optional testing the module would like these other modules:

  Test::Pod
  Test::Pod::Coverage

